<li id="cite_note-Wong_07-4"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Wong_07_4-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFWong.2C_William2007">Wong, William (April 27, 2007). "<a href="http://www.elecdesign.com/Articles/Index.cfm?AD=1&amp;ArticleID=15350" class="external text" title="http://www.elecdesign.com/Articles/Index.cfm?AD=1&amp;ArticleID=15350" rel="nofollow">I/O, I/O, It's Off to Virtual Work We Go</a>". <i>Electronic Design</i><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.elecdesign.com/Articles/Index.cfm?AD=1&amp;ArticleID=15350" class="external free" title="http://www.elecdesign.com/Articles/Index.cfm?AD=1&amp;ArticleID=15350" rel="nofollow">http://www.elecdesign.com/Articles/Index.cfm?AD=1&amp;ArticleID=15350</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=I%2FO%2C+I%2FO%2C+It%27s+Off+to+Virtual+Work+We+Go&amp;rft.jtitle=Electronic+Design&amp;rft.aulast=Wong%2C+William&amp;rft.au=Wong%2C+William&amp;rft.date=April+27%2C+2007&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.elecdesign.com%2FArticles%2FIndex.cfm%3FAD%3D1%26ArticleID%3D15350&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Microkernel"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
