<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFBlack.2C_D.L..2C_Golub.2C_D.B..2C_Julin.2C_D.P..2C_Rashid.2C_R.F..2C_Draves.2C_R.P..2C_Dean.2C_R.W..2C_Forin.2C_A..2C_Barrera.2C_J..2C_Tokuda.2C_H..2C_Malan.2C_G..2C_and_Bohman.2C_D.1992">Black, D.L., Golub, D.B., Julin, D.P., Rashid, R.F., Draves, R.P., Dean, R.W., Forin, A., Barrera, J., Tokuda, H., Malan, G., and Bohman, D. (March 1992). "Microkernel Operating System Architecture and Mach". <i>J. Of Information Processing</i> <b>14(4)</b>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Microkernel+Operating+System+Architecture+and+Mach&amp;rft.jtitle=J.+Of+Information+Processing&amp;rft.aulast=Black%2C+D.L.%2C+Golub%2C+D.B.%2C+Julin%2C+D.P.%2C+Rashid%2C+R.F.%2C+Draves%2C+R.P.%2C+Dean%2C+R.W.%2C+Forin%2C+A.%2C+Barrera%2C+J.%2C+Tokuda%2C+H.%2C+Malan%2C+G.%2C+and+Bohman%2C+D.&amp;rft.au=Black%2C+D.L.%2C+Golub%2C+D.B.%2C+Julin%2C+D.P.%2C+Rashid%2C+R.F.%2C+Draves%2C+R.P.%2C+Dean%2C+R.W.%2C+Forin%2C+A.%2C+Barrera%2C+J.%2C+Tokuda%2C+H.%2C+Malan%2C+G.%2C+and+Bohman%2C+D.&amp;rft.date=March+1992&amp;rft.volume=14%284%29&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Microkernel"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span> - the basic Mach reference.</li>
</ul>
</li>
